<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Café Sundae Menu</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f1ea;
            color: #4e342e;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #6d4c41;
            color: white;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .menu-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #795548;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6d4c41;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .menu-item {
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc;
        }
        .menu-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .menu-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #5d4037;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .menu-item p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .price {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6d4c41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        Café Sundae Menu
    </header>

    <div class="menu-container">
        <h2>Classic & Traditional Sundaes</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Hot Fudge Sundae <span class="price">₹180</span></h3>
            <p>Vanilla ice cream topped with warm chocolate fudge, whipped cream, and a cherry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Caramel Sundae <span class="price">₹170</span></h3>
            <p>Ice cream drizzled with rich caramel sauce, often with nuts or toffee bits.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Creative & Unique Sundaes</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Turtle Sundae <span class="price">₹200</span></h3>
            <p>Vanilla ice cream with caramel, hot fudge, and pecans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Rocky Road Sundae <span class="price">₹210</span></h3>
            <p>Chocolate ice cream with marshmallows, nuts, and chocolate syrup.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h2>International-Inspired Sundaes</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Affogato <span class="price">₹190</span></h3>
            <p>A scoop of vanilla ice cream "drowned" in a shot of hot espresso.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Matcha Green Tea Sundae <span class="price">₹220</span></h3>
            <p>Green tea ice cream with red bean paste and mochi.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
